Download logo Today, President Abdel-Fattah El-Sisi, the President of the Republic, the Supreme Commander of the Armed Forces, led the military funeral of Assistant to the President for National and Strategic Projects and Former Prime Minister, Sherif Ismail, at El-Mosheer Tantawy Mosque, New Cairo.  President El-Sisi offered his condolences to the late Ismail’s family. The President described him as one of the finest patriotic symbols, who left behind a journey full of work and dedication with all sincerity, at a critical stage of the homeland’s history. President El-Sisi confirmed that this is greatly appreciated by Egypt and its great people. Distributed by APO Group on behalf of The Presidency, The Arab Republic of Egypt.